text: Klara may refer to: * Klara, a female given name, see Clara (given name) * Klara (radio), a classical-music radio station in Belgium * Klara (singer), birth name Klára Vytisková (born 1985), Czech singer * Klara (Stockholm), an area of central Stockholm * Klarälven (the Klar River, or River Klara) in Sweden * VinFast Klara, an electric scooter made in Vietnam *
